<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='560000' id='t-560000'>And the 80 percent zone is a no-carrot and no-stick zone.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='564000' id='t-564000'>The costs of running the institution mean that you cannot</span>
